{"tid":749520,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日係我隻狗死忌","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T17:08:00.000Z","uid":133824,"like":108,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0a893d35a98f9744e1c7506b8d71f48c8d8842","tid":749520,"uid":133824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"上年既琴日佢走左，成家都好傷心同一個親人走左無分別<br />\n琴日係相簿同fb睇番佢既相同片，之後呆左半個鐘諗番佢點跑跑跳跳，嗲我地扭抱<br />\n呢11年除左我，連我阿爹阿娘都當佢孫咁錫，希望養緊寵物既你好好咁陪下佢地，因為佢地既世界真係得你地<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/134553_55408a73762a9638a303c2e06874c6b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F134553_55408a73762a9638a303c2e06874c6b1.png&h=c4d53fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n送佢走果時好似訓左咁，真係有一刻以為佢會突然間起番身又嗲我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/134820_b8eb7f33c8d558caff907f8f1236d7eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F134820_b8eb7f33c8d558caff907f8f1236d7eb.png&h=14c0a892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 請所有養緊寵物既你唔好話棄養就棄養！</span>"},{"pid":"5ef476eebf07280e5d15aa88d09c4952f617321e","tid":749520,"uid":156940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"最後嗰一刻嘅畫面係好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf0749600cb27ceb0d00c98f1be8d69567f02b1","tid":749520,"uid":4780,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好傷心，佢去到彩虹橋日日跑黎跑去好開心嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0389f467f4d8bc699da48190a459fc09e16d3e3","tid":749520,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"r